Lifeways Care Provider May Be Put Up for Sale, Sunday Times Says

-- B y   K a r e n   E e u w e n s
-- 
2011-08-21T08:52:28Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-21/lifeways-care-provider-may-be-put-up-for-sale-sunday-times-says.html
Lifeways Community Care Ltd. may be
sold after its owner August Equity hired Rothschild to manage a
strategic review of the specialist-care provider, the Sunday
Times reported, without saying where it got the information.  Lifeways may fetch about 200 million pounds ($329 million)
to 250 million pounds, according to analysts, the U.K. newspaper
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Karen Eeuwens in  London  
 keeuwens@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Francisco Marcelino at 
 mdeoliveira@bloomberg.net . 